set_dial                              macro                             set_dial

NAME
     sseett__ddiiaall - define the dial position of a motor

SYNOPSIS

     sseett__ddiiaall mmoottoorr vvaalluuee

DESCRIPTION

     The sseett__ddiiaall macro is used to set the dial position to vvaalluuee for one mmoottoorr.

     The macro use the built-in functions cchhgg__ddiiaall(()) and cchhgg__ooffffsseett(()).

EXAMPLE

     sseett__ddiiaall tthh 00

